---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import RelatedWorkflows from '../../components/RelatedWorkflows.astro';
import Screenshot from '../../components/Screenshot.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Workflows', url: '/workflows' },
  { name: 'Invoicing & Expenses', url: '/workflows/invoicing-expenses' }
];

const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'What payment methods can I track?',
    answer: 'BreederHQ tracks Cash, Check, Credit Card, Debit Card, ACH, Wire Transfer, PayPal, Venmo, and Zelle. Each payment can include a reference number for reconciliation.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Can clients pay through the platform?',
    answer: 'Yes. With Stripe integration, clients can pay invoices directly through their portal. You can also create Stripe invoices that are sent via email with a payment link.'
  },
  {
    question: 'What expense categories are available?',
    answer: 'Twelve categories: Veterinary, Supplies, Food, Grooming, Breeding, Facility, Marketing, Labor, Insurance, Registration, Travel, and Other. Each expense can be linked to specific animals.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Can I export financial data?',
    answer: 'Yes. Export invoices, payments, and expenses to CSV with configurable columns. Works with spreadsheets, accounting software, or your CPA.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Does this replace accounting software?',
    answer: 'BreederHQ handles breeder-specific invoicing and expense tracking. For full accounting (tax returns, depreciation, etc.), you may still want dedicated accounting software. Data exports make integration easy.'
  },
  {
    question: 'How do breeding plan financial rollups work?',
    answer: 'Each breeding plan shows total revenue, deposit timing (before/after birth), and average pricing. See the financial picture for each litter or group of offspring at a glance.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Can I log expenses from my phone?',
    answer: 'Yes. The BreederHQ Mobile Companion app — the on-the-go partner to the web app — is built for exactly this. Snap a photo of any receipt with your phone camera, enter the amount, category, and which animal or breeding plan it belongs to, and save. Food purchases can link to a Food Product so nutrition costs roll up automatically. Everything syncs instantly to the web app.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Can I create invoices from my phone?',
    answer: 'No — invoice creation and Stripe invoice management is intentionally a web-app task, where you get the full line-item editor, tax rules, and payment-link workflow. The Mobile Companion is scoped to quick-capture work like snapping receipts, logging expenses, and reviewing invoices on the go. Setup work belongs in the web app; in-the-moment capture belongs in the companion.'
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Invoicing & Expenses, Built for Breeders | BreederHQ"
  description="Create invoices with deposits and line items, track 9 payment methods including Stripe, and log expenses across 12 categories. Snap receipts on the go in the BreederHQ Mobile Companion app."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
  faqs={faqs}
>
  <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:absolute focus:top-4 focus:left-4 focus:z-50 focus:px-4 focus:py-2 focus:bg-white focus:text-black focus:shadow-lg focus:rounded">
    Skip to content
  </a>

  <main id="main-content">
  <nav class="breadcrumb py-4 px-4 bg-gray-50" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-sm">
      <li><a href="/" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Home</a></li>
      <li class="text-gray-400">›</li>
      <li><a href="/workflows" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Workflows</a></li>
      <li class="text-gray-400">›</li>
      <li aria-current="page" class="text-gray-600">Invoicing & Expenses</li>
    </ol>
  </nav>

  <!-- Section 1: Hero -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Invoicing & Expenses, Built for Breeders.</h1>

      <aside class="tldr-box bg-gray-100 border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] p-6 my-8 rounded" role="complementary" aria-label="Page summary">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">TL;DR</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Full invoicing and expense tracking connected to your animals, offspring groups, and breeding plans. Create invoices with deposits, service fees, goods, and discounts. Track payments via 9 methods including Stripe. Log expenses across 12 categories — and when you're at the vet, the feed store, or the show grounds, snap receipt photos right from the BreederHQ Mobile Companion app so paperwork gets captured as it happens. See financial dashboards with outstanding balances, month-to-date metrics, and per-group rollups. Export to CSV for your accountant.
        </p>
      </aside>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        "Did they pay the deposit?" "What's their remaining balance?" "How much have I spent on vet bills this year?"
      </p>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        You already answer these questions every week. BreederHQ keeps the invoices, payments, and receipts organized and connected to the animals and breeding plans they belong to, so the answer is always a quick look away.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <Screenshot
          id="finance-invoices"
          alt="Invoice ledger in BreederHQ showing paid invoices with deposits and outstanding balances"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: The Problem -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">You already run this like a business. Here's where it gets complicated.</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        You care about the numbers. The challenge is keeping them organized across multiple animals, breeding plans, and payment methods:
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Handwritten deposit logs that don't sync with anything</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Venmo payments with no record of what they're for</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Expenses scattered across receipts, bank statements, and memory</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>No easy way to see if a litter or group was profitable until tax time</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Awkward conversations confirming what a client owes and what they've already paid</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] p-6 rounded">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold">
          Generic accounting software doesn't speak breeder. It doesn't link invoices to specific litters or offspring groups, track deposits by waitlist position, or show revenue per breeding plan.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: Invoicing -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Professional Invoicing for Breeders</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Create clear, professional invoices that clients can understand and pay:
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Invoice Line Item Types</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm font-medium mr-3">Deposit</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Initial deposits, progress payments</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm font-medium mr-3">Service Fee</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Stud fees, training, photography</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm font-medium mr-3">Goods</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Animal price, supplies, merchandise</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm font-medium mr-3">Discount</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Early payment, returning client</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm font-medium mr-3">Tax</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Sales tax where applicable</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">📄 Invoice Status Tracking</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Draft:</strong> Working on it, not sent</li>
            <li><strong>Issued:</strong> Sent to client</li>
            <li><strong>Partially Paid:</strong> Some payment received</li>
            <li><strong>Paid:</strong> Fully paid</li>
            <li><strong>Overdue:</strong> Past due date</li>
            <li><strong>Void:</strong> Canceled</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">🔗 Link to Breeding Data</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>• Anchor invoices to specific animals</li>
            <li>• Link to offspring groups (litters, foals, kids, lambs, kits)</li>
            <li>• Associate with breeding plans</li>
            <li>• Connect to service codes</li>
            <li>• Attach supporting documents</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)]">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">💳 Stripe Integration</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          Connect your Stripe account for seamless online payments:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <li>• Create Stripe invoices directly from BreederHQ</li>
          <li>• Clients pay via link in email or portal</li>
          <li>• Automatic payment status sync</li>
          <li>• Download PDFs for signed invoices</li>
          <li>• Void invoices when needed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: Payment Tracking -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Track Every Payment Method</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Clients pay however is convenient for them. BreederHQ tracks it all:
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-5 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-2">💵</div>
          <div class="font-medium">Cash</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-2">📝</div>
          <div class="font-medium">Check</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-2">💳</div>
          <div class="font-medium">Credit Card</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🏦</div>
          <div class="font-medium">ACH</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🔗</div>
          <div class="font-medium">Wire</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🅿️</div>
          <div class="font-medium">PayPal</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-2">📱</div>
          <div class="font-medium">Venmo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-2">⚡</div>
          <div class="font-medium">Zelle</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-2">💰</div>
          <div class="font-medium">Debit Card</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Each payment record includes date, amount, method, reference number (for check numbers, transaction IDs, etc.), and automatic invoice balance updates.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Expense Tracking -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Know Where Your Money Goes</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Track every breeding expense with categories designed for your business:
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">🏥 Veterinary</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Exams, testing, procedures, medications</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">📦 Supplies</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Birthing supplies, collars, halters, crates</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">🍖 Food</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Kibble, raw, supplements</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">✂️ Grooming</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Professional grooming, supplies</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">🧬 Breeding</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Stud fees, live cover, artificial insemination, embryo transfer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">🏠 Facility</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Barns, kennels, fencing, utilities</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">📣 Marketing</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Website, photos, advertising</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">👷 Labor</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Help, training, contractors</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">🛡️ Insurance</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Liability, health, property</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">📋 Registration</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Registry fees, microchips, licenses</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">🚗 Travel</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Shows, pickups, vet visits</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">📁 Other</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Everything else</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Expense Features</h3>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li>• Link expenses to specific animals or breeding plans</li>
          <li>• Track vendor information</li>
          <li>• Attach receipt images (upload or camera capture)</li>
          <li>• Filter by date range, category, animal</li>
          <li>• Export to CSV for tax prep</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)]">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">📱 Log Expenses On the Go (Mobile Companion)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          The BreederHQ Mobile Companion app makes expense capture something you can do the moment it happens — exactly the kind of away-from-the-desk task it's built for. Walk out of the vet, the feed store, or the show grounds and have the receipt filed before you're back in the truck:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <li>• Snap a photo of the receipt with your phone camera</li>
          <li>• Enter the amount, category, and which animal or breeding plan it belongs to</li>
          <li>• Food purchases can link to a Food Product so nutrition costs roll up automatically</li>
          <li>• Syncs instantly to the web so everything is in one place for tax time</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6: Financial Dashboard -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">See Your Financial Picture at a Glance</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        The financial dashboard gives you instant visibility into your breeding business:
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6">Dashboard Metrics</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-4">
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Outstanding Invoices</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold">Total amount owed to you</div>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Month-to-Date Invoiced</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold">Revenue this month</div>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Month-to-Date Collected</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold">Payments received</div>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-500 pl-4">
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Month-to-Date Expenses</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold">Costs this month</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)]">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">📊 Breeding Plan Financial Rollups</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          Each breeding plan shows aggregated financial data:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <li>• Total revenue per litter or group</li>
          <li>• Deposit timing analysis (before/after birth)</li>
          <li>• Average price per offspring</li>
          <li>• Expenses linked to the breeding plan</li>
          <li>• Profit and loss visibility</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Clear Numbers, Connected to Your Animals.</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Invoicing, payments, and expenses in one place, with mobile receipt capture so the paperwork keeps up with you.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=breeder_dashboard" class="bg-white text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:opacity-90 inline-block">
          Get Started Free
        </a>
        <a href="/workflows/client-portal" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-primary inline-block">
          See Client Portal →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 faq-section">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>What payment methods can I track?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>BreederHQ tracks Cash, Check, Credit Card, Debit Card, ACH, Wire Transfer, PayPal, Venmo, and Zelle. Each payment can include a reference number for reconciliation.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Can clients pay through the platform?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. With Stripe integration, clients can pay invoices directly through their portal. You can also create Stripe invoices that are sent via email with a payment link.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Does this replace accounting software?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>BreederHQ handles breeder-specific invoicing and expense tracking. For full accounting (tax returns, depreciation, etc.), you may still want dedicated accounting software. Data exports make integration easy.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Can I export financial data?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. Export invoices, payments, and expenses to CSV with configurable columns. Works with spreadsheets, accounting software, or your CPA.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Can I log expenses from my phone?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. The BreederHQ Mobile Companion app — the on-the-go partner to the web app — is built for exactly this. Snap a photo of any receipt with your phone camera, enter the amount, category, and which animal or breeding plan it belongs to, and save. Food purchases can link to a Food Product so nutrition costs roll up automatically. Everything syncs instantly to the web app.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Can I create invoices from my phone?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>No — invoice creation and Stripe invoice management is intentionally a web-app task, where you get the full line-item editor, tax rules, and payment-link workflow. The Mobile Companion is scoped to quick-capture work like snapping receipts, logging expenses, and reviewing invoices on the go. Setup work belongs in the web app; in-the-moment capture belongs in the companion.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
